metadata.name: Aki Anniversary 記念日おめでとう
metadata.description:
Aki fell in love in the blossom, she visit Maruyama Park every year wearing a kimono, a traditional Japanese garment, and it is commonly worn in events such as weddings, graduation and celebration. She used to share a sushi oke kaza with her beloved husband on this special day. Unfortunately, due to a car accident, he lost his life and since then Aki, celebrates their wedding anniversary in the blossom. The beautiful nature represents his presence as the mysterious energy surrounding them with butterflies to remain the devoted love from him.  

Resolution: 5616 x 3744 Pixels
Format: PNG
Digital Print 31” x 21” inches 400dpi+ 
Quality: 4k HD Quality
